name: We Cannot Create Anything That Is Unnatural
description:
Told from the perspective of a digital oracle created in human image, the piece stutters its way through cyclic synth motifs with elastic tempo, pondering universality and the natural entropy of everything.

~~~~~~

A 49 second .mp4 excerpt from "Course Correct", a music video by uuskhy x SIFI.
